OL,4,T#######################################
OL,5, Boris Johnson has appointed the former 
OL,6, Tesco chief executive, Sir Dave Lewis, 
OL,7, to advise on how to fix the supply     
OL,8, chain crisis that has led to petrol and
OL,9, other shortages.                       
OL,11,FIt comes as the Office for National    
OL,12,FStatistics found one in six UK adults  
OL,13,Fsaid they had been unable to buy       
OL,14,Fessential foods in the last fortnight. 
OL,16,FThe recent fuel crisis was caused in   
OL,17,Fpart by a shortage of lorry drivers.   
OL,19,FBrexit and the pandemic have both      
OL,20,Fcontributed to labour shortages.       
